The '''Third General Survey''' was an exploration of spiral arms of the [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] launched on [[145 BBY]] by the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]]. It was responsible for finding the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Brath Qella]]. However, due to the [[Declaration of a New Order|rise]] of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]], it was never completed and Brath Qella went unexplored.

The mission had reported Brath Qella as a temperate [[Planet/Legends|world]], with a population of seven million, and a primary ecosystem rated provisionally at complexity two. However when the planet was revisited in [[16 ABY/Legends|16 ABY]] by the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]], a third of the planet's landmass was glaciated and its people were gone.<ref name="Shield of Lies">''[[Shield of Lies]]''</ref>

